    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, with every system functioning exactly as intended and a comprehensive service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously preserved and cared for at the highest level.",
